OL,3,CMore than 4,500 police officers
OL,4,Cspecially trained to investigate rape
OL,6,FThe Home Secretary vows to put more
OL,7,Fsex offenders behind bars as police
OL,8,Freceive specialist training, as Liz
OL,9,FSummers reports.
OL,11,FThousands of police officers have been
OL,12,Fspecially trained to investigate
OL,13,Freports of rape, in a bid to overhaul
OL,14,Fhow rape and sexual offences are
OL,15,Fhandled.
OL,17,FIt's being described as a "significant
OL,18,Fmilestone" by the Home Secretary, who
OL,19,Fhas vowed to put more sex offenders
OL,20,Fbehind bars.
