OL,3,CMore than 4,500 police officers
OL,4,Cspecially trained to investigate rape
OL,6,FMore than 4,500 police officers in
OL,7,FEngland and Wales have now completed
OL,8,Fthe specialist training, according to
OL,9,Fthe College of Policing.
OL,11,FThis included officers in each of the
OL,12,F43 forces. The number of police
OL,13,Ftrained per force has not been
OL,14,Fdisclosed.
OL,16,FThis is more than double a target set
OL,17,Fby the Government to train up 2,000 by
OL,18,FMay.
