OL,6,FMr Cleverly said exceeding the target
OL,7,Fwas "another significant milestone in
OL,8,Four efforts to transform the way the
OL,9,Fcriminal justice system deals with
OL,10,Frape and sexual offences".
OL,12,FHe described the training as a "very
OL,13,Fpositive step" and one which will
OL,14,Fimprove "the police's ability".
OL,16,FHe added: "We have gone further than
OL,17,Fever before to protect women and
OL,18,Fgirls, but we are not slowing down.
