OL,6,F"Building on the progress we have made
OL,7,Fso far, we will continue to drive up
OL,8,Fprosecutions, protect victims and put
OL,9,Fmore sex offenders behind bars," he
OL,10,Fadded.
OL,12,FNew police recruits will also face
OL,13,Fmandatory training on responding to
OL,14,Frape and sexual offences.
