OL,3,CMore than 4,500 police officers
OL,4,Cspecially trained to investigate rape
OL,6,FThere were 2,558 prosecutions last
OL,7,Fyear. This is an increase of 44% from
OL,8,F2022 when there were 1,778
OL,9,Fprosecutions.
OL,11,FLast year there were 636 convictions
OL,12,Fand 627 sentences for adult rape.
OL,14,FBut according to Home Office figures
OL,15,Ffor the same period, the proportion of
OL,16,Fsuspects being taken to court for rape
OL,17,Fis still among the lowest levels
OL,18,Frecorded, with a charge rate of 2.6%.
